                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18290409-51-off304 t18290409-51-cd305"></join>, 3 loaves of bread, value 2s. 3d.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t18290409-51-victim562" type="victimName">
                     John 
                     Turk
                  <interp inst="t18290409-51-victim562" type="surname" value="Turk"></interp>
